SR NO. 142 ENROLLED
WHEREAS, Braxton's success serves as an inspiration to others, reflecting the values
of faith, hard work, and determination instilled through his family, education, and
community; and
WHEREAS, Braxton represents the city of Walker and Livingston Parish with
excellence and distinction through his outstanding accomplishment as reserve champion of
the 2026 Hondo Rodeo Fest in New Orleans, Louisiana.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend and congratulate Braxton Whitesell on earning the title of reserve
champion at the 2026 Hondo Rodeo Fest.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to
Braxton Whitesell.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
